feat: add /health and /ready endpoints for k8s probes (he-2p6)

/health returns 200 if the process is alive (liveness probe).
/ready returns 200 only when DB is reachable, at least one LLM provider
responds, and at least one channel is registered. Returns JSON with
per-component status breakdown. Both endpoints bypass API key auth.

